### 🔄 10. TEST VALIDATION
### ============================================

### 10.1 ❌ Giảm giá âm (Expected: 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/invoices
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 0
    }
  ],
  "discountAmount": -5000,
  "paidAmount": 50000,
  "paymentMethod": "CASH"
}

### 10.2 ❌ Số tiền thanh toán âm (Expected: 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/invoices
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 0
    }
  ],
  "paidAmount": -10000,
  "paymentMethod": "CASH"
}

### 10.3 ❌ Note quá dài (Expected: 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/invoices
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 0
    }
  ],
  "paidAmount": 50000,
  "paymentMethod": "CASH",
  "note": ""
}

